OL,3,CMother disappointed following plans to
OL,4,Ccut boarding at special education
OL,5,Cschool
OL,7,FA mother from Cornwall who sends her
OL,8,Fteenage son to a special education
OL,9,Fschool has said she is disappointed by
OL,10,Fthe council's plan to withdraw funding
OL,11,Ffor overnight boarding.
OL,13,FEarlier this month, Cornwall Council
OL,14,Fannounced it is planning to withdraw
OL,15,Ffunding for residential stays at
OL,16,FPencalenick School, in Truro.
OL,18,FThe council says it is planning to use
OL,19,Fthe money to create more day places at
OL,20,Fspecial education schools.
