OL,7,FMs De-Bargeton added that Louis enjoys
OL,8,Fboarding at the school once a week as
OL,9,Fhe has to travel more than three hours
OL,10,Fevery day to get there.
OL,12,F"Louis gets picked up at 7:30am and
OL,13,Fdoesn't get home until 4:30pm, because
OL,14,Fthey pick up other students en route,
OL,15,Fso for him not to have to go in the
OL,16,Ftaxi every single day makes a really
OL,17,Fbig difference because it's such a
OL,18,Flong day," she said.
