OL,5,Cschool
OL,7,FPencalenick School is the only special
OL,8,Feducation school in Cornwall that
OL,9,Foffers boarding.
OL,11,FBut Cornwall Council is proposing to
OL,12,Fwithdraw its #563,000 budget for
OL,13,Fovernight stays in order to create
OL,14,Fadditional day places in special
OL,15,Feducation schools.
