OL,3,CMother disappointed following plans to
OL,4,Ccut boarding at special education
OL,5,Cschool
OL,7,FThe council says there are currently
OL,8,Fmore than 4000 children in Cornwall
OL,9,Fwith Education, Health and Care Plans
OL,10,F(EHCP), meaning the need for day
OL,11,Fplaces at special education schools is
OL,12,Fincreasing.
OL,14,FA Cornwall Council spokesperson said:
OL,15,F"We have to ensure funding reflects
OL,16,Fthe special education required to meet
OL,17,Fcurrent and forecast need, and
OL,18,Fcontinuing to fund overnight provision
OL,19,Ftherefore no longer presents value for
OL,20,Fmoney."
