OL,5,Cschool
OL,7,FCornwall Council has launched a
OL,8,Fconsultation on the proposals to
OL,9,Freallocate SEND funding.
OL,11,FThe Special Partnership Trust, which
OL,12,Fruns Pencalenick School, said they
OL,13,Fwill be directly supporting pupils,
OL,14,Fparents and staff throughout the
OL,15,Fconsultation process.
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the trust said:
OL,18,F"Throughout this consultation, we will
OL,19,Fcontinue to deliver a high-quality,
OL,20,FSEN educational residential offer
OL,21,Funtil further notice."
